First fill up the 5-quart jug, next fill up the 3-quart jug with the water in the 5-quart jug.
Then there are 2 quarts of water in the 5-quart jug. Then empty the 3-quart jug and fill the 
3-quart jug with the remaining 2 quarts of water in the 5-quart jug. Then fill up the 5-quart
jug. Then fill up the 3-quart jug with the water in the 5-quart jug. Then we have 4 quarts of 
water in the 5-quart jug.